{"tid":1897103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[撐港台]港台：《頭條新聞》諷刺時弊非嚴肅新聞　顧委會陳建強不滿沒解釋如何準確持平","createTime":"2020-02-25T13:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T03:17:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2d7b1917cff816278e503a611d03d0c0c2f231ad","tid":1897103,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"警務處長日前去信廣播處長梁家榮，稱對港台節目《頭條新聞》「以嘲諷形式抹黑警隊」表示遺憾，港台顧問委員會（顧委會）去信港台並要求就事件解釋。本報取得港台今日（25日）向顧委會回信，內容強調港台有履行《香港電台約章》訂明公共目的及使命，並指出《頭條新聞》是諷刺時弊節目（satirical show），「任何理性的人都不太可能視之為嚴肅新聞」。顧委會主席陳建強稱對港台回應的態度和內容「不滿和遺憾」。<br />\n<strong><br />\n本報取得港台回信，發信日期是今日，信中稱港台欣賞（appreciated）所有政府部門、包括警隊在抗疫的付出，但指出《頭條新聞》自1989年啟播以來，一直被公眾視為非新聞類作品（a non-news genre），認為任何理性的人（reasonable persons）都不太可能（quite unlikely）視之為嚴肅新聞。</strong>信中又提到港台一直以來都提供各類型的節目，以履行《香港電台約章》中公共目的及使命或編輯方針，包括提供準確而持平的新聞報道、資訊、觀點及分析。<br />\n<br />\n陳建強接受本報查詢時稱，確認收到港台回信，又說顧委會不滿港台只在信中稱履行準確持平的編輯方針，「但沒有清楚解釋如何做到」，質疑回信由助理廣播處長（電視及機構業務）區麗雅代行，而非梁家榮親自解釋。他說顧委會將盡快開會商討如何跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200225/s00001/1582635548241/%e6%b8%af%e5%8f%b0-%e3%80%8a%e9%a0%ad%e6%a2%9d%e6%96%b0%e8%81%9e%e3%80%8b%e8%ab%b7%e5%88%ba%e6%99%82%e5%bc%8a%e9%9d%9e%e5%9a%b4%e8%82%85%e6%96%b0%e8%81%9e-%e9%a1%a7%e5%a7%94%e6%9c%83%e9%99%b3%e5%bb%ba%e5%bc%b7%e4%b8%8d%e6%bb%bf%e6%b2%92%e8%a7%a3%e9%87%8b%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e6%ba%96%e7%a2%ba%e6%8c%81%e5%b9%b3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200225%2Fs00001%2F1582635548241%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%258f%25b0-%25e3%2580%258a%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e6%25a2%259d%25e6%2596%25b0%25e8%2581%259e%25e3%2580%258b%25e8%25ab%25b7%25e5%2588%25ba%25e6%2599%2582%25e5%25bc%258a%25e9%259d%259e%25e5%259a%25b4%25e8%2582%2585%25e6%2596%25b0%25e8%2581%259e-%25e9%25a1%25a7%25e5%25a7%2594%25e6%259c%2583%25e9%2599%25b3%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%25bb%25bf%25e6%25b2%2592%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e9%2587%258b%25e5%25a6%2582%25e4%25bd%2595%25e6%25ba%2596%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e6%258c%2581%25e5%25b9%25b3&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=b6dad087\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200225%2Fs00001%2F1582635548241%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e5%258f%25b0-%25e3%2580%258a%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e6%25a2%259d%25e6%2596%25b0%25e8%2581%259e%25e3%2580%258b%25e8%25ab%25b7%25e5%2588%25ba%25e6%2599%2582%25e5%25bc%258a%25e9%259d%259e%25e5%259a%25b4%25e8%2582%2585%25e6%2596%25b0%25e8%2581%259e-%25e9%25a1%25a7%25e5%25a7%2594%25e6%259c%2583%25e9%2599%25b3%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%25bb%25bf%25e6%25b2%2592%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e9%2587%258b%25e5%25a6%2582%25e4%25bd%2595%25e6%25ba%2596%25e7%25a2%25ba%25e6%258c%2581%25e5%25b9%25b3&h=ceb8bdce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200225/s00001/1582635548241/%e6%b8%af%e5%8f%b0-%e3%80%8a%e9%a0%ad%e6%a2%9d%e6%96%b0%e8%81%9e%e3%80%8b%e8%ab%b7%e5%88%ba%e6%99%82%e5%bc%8a%e9%9d%9e%e5%9a%b4%e8%82%85%e6%96%b0%e8%81%9e-%e9%a1%a7%e5%a7%94%e6%9c%83%e9%99%b3%e5%bb%ba%e5%bc%b7%e4%b8%8d%e6%bb%bf%e6%b2%92%e8%a7%a3%e9%87%8b%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e6%ba%96%e7%a2%ba%e6%8c%81%e5%b9%b3</a>"},{"pid":"a350a6895e3a07052c75d0ac4f3968d799210c65","tid":1897103,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T13:50:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae078a7b5f5cc43e2e26d9724a9cb0b299443f2b","tid":1897103,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"幫港台反cup"},{"pid":"aacd26e22974f415667beacd51e30bc473710ba0","tid":1897103,"uid":225130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:22:24.000Z","msg":"有個句講個句唔係持平？<br />\n無錯，只可以支持警隊先係持平～"},{"pid":"7ce2604e4ddf5088cdff65425513fac239579534","tid":1897103,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"陳建強乜水"},{"pi